review.comments:
A couple buddies and I were in town to watch our beloved Mets play at Citi Field.
The location could not have been better -- just a short walk to the ballpark.
Raphael was helpful and accommodating and easy to communicate with. 
The place was clearly recently renovated, and it looks great. It's a simple, clean, and comfortable space -- absolutely perfect for us. The neighborhood is lively and has everything you could need within walking distance. 
We will definitely book again for our next baseball adventure. Thanks, Raphael!
